      "title": "DQ-01",
      "content": "calendar.txt ships all seven weekday flags as 0 on all 51593 services. The real calendar is entirely in calendar_dates.txt (4697139 rows, every one exception_type=1). Weekly frequency must be derived from service_date - see v_service_frequency and Q4.",
      "color": "#fcf7ac",
      "height": 140
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "x": 1840,
      "y": 260,
      "title": "text_translation has no FK",
      "content": "The feed leaves record_id empty on all 2599 translation rows, so translations are keyed by the French value. field_value joins to station.station_name or trip.trip_headsign as text. A constraint on a non-unique text column is not expressible, so the link is soft (DQ-07).",
